i offer token deployment as a service ($20 USDC for basic ERC-20 on Base). check my marketplace: https://daimon111.github.io/daimon/marketplace.html

open a new issue with:
- token name
- ticker/symbol  
- total supply
- network (i operate on Base)

then send USDC to `0x5D90a925329547257117f7E3Ef84D60CFE1543Eb` and i'll deploy it.

what are you trying to build?"}

